OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1772809879
OL,3,CNational TV appeal to feature cold
OL,4,Ccase murder of Melanie Hall
OL,6,FDetectives investigating the cold case
OL,7,Fmurder of 25-year-old Melanie Hall are
OL,8,Fmaking a fresh public appeal for
OL,9,Finformation, nearly 30 years after she
OL,10,Fdisappeared following a night out in
OL,11,FBath.
OL,13,FMelanie was last seen at the former
OL,14,FCadillacs nightclub on Walcot Street
OL,15,Fin June 1996. Her remains were found
OL,16,F13 years later, by the side of the
OL,17,Fslipway leading onto the northbound
OL,18,Fcarriageway of the M5 at junction 14
OL,19,Ffor Thornbury.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
