FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43802
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1772809879
OL,3,CNational TV appeal to feature cold
OL,4,Ccase murder of Melanie Hall
OL,6,FShe had suffered extensive head
OL,7,Finjuries and was wrapped in black bin
OL,8,Fliners, tied with blue rope.
OL,10,FDetective Chief Inspector Ben Lavender
OL,11,Fof Avon and Somerset Police, who's
OL,12,Fleading the case, will appear on
OL,13,FCrimewatch on Wednesday 4 March. The
OL,14,Fprogramme will also include an
OL,15,Finterview with Melanie's father Steve
OL,16,Fand sister Dominique.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
