OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43803
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1772809879
OL,3,CNational TV appeal to feature cold
OL,4,Ccase murder of Melanie Hall
OL,6,FAlongside the TV appeal, Crimestoppers
OL,7,Fhas announced it's putting up a reward
OL,8,Fof up to #20,000 for information
OL,9,Fleading to the arrest and conviction
OL,10,Fof the person or people responsible
OL,11,Ffor Melanie's murder.
OL,13,FDCI Lavender said: "The murder of
OL,14,FMelanie Hall is one of the longest-
OL,15,Frunning and highest-profile
OL,16,Finvestigations ever carried out by
OL,17,FAvon and Somerset Police, with
OL,18,Fhundreds of officers working on the
OL,19,Fcase over the years.
OL,26,@uD@TOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
