OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43805
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1772809879
OL,3,CNational TV appeal to feature cold
OL,4,Ccase murder of Melanie Hall
OL,6,F"As we approach this significant
OL,7,Fanniversary, I want people to think
OL,8,Fback to the weekend of Saturday 8 and
OL,9,FSunday 9 June in 1996. England were
OL,10,Fplaying Switzerland in the opening
OL,11,Fgame of the Euros, and the centre of
OL,12,FBath was exceptionally busy.
OL,14,F"Melanie had spent an evening with her
OL,15,Fboyfriend and friends and went to the
OL,16,Fformer Cadillacs nightclub. The last
OL,17,Fconfirmed sighting of her was at
OL,18,F1.10am on Sunday, 9 June, when her
OL,19,Ffriends left the club. She was sitting
OL,20,Fby the side of the dancefloor on her
OL,21,Fown.
OL,26,@nD@AOUvD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43806
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1772809879
OL,3,CNational TV appeal to feature cold
OL,4,Ccase murder of Melanie Hall
OL,6,F"We believe there's a strong
OL,7,Fpossibility Melanie left the nightclub
OL,8,Fwith her killer, as a coat she'd
OL,9,Fchecked into a cloakroom was
OL,10,Fcollected, but she could have met them
OL,11,Foutside or got into a car."
OL,13,FDCI Lavender said the discovery of
OL,14,FMelanie's remains by the side of the
OL,15,FM5 at junction 14 in 2009 only
OL,16,Fprovided some answers.
OL,18,FHe said: "The location whereMelanie's
OL,19,Fremains were foundremainsa key focus
OL,20,Fforus.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@[O]zD@JOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
