OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,439,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43807
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1772809879
OL,3,CNational TV appeal to feature cold
OL,4,Ccase murder of Melanie Hall
OL,6,F"We'rekeeping anopenmind as to when
OL,7,FMelanie's body was dumped at this
OL,8,Flocation. Thiscould have been in the
OL,9,Fhours after she went missing, or the
OL,10,Fdays following.
OL,12,F"Melanie's remains were found without
OL,13,Fher clothing or items she had with her
OL,14,Fon the night she went missing. She was
OL,15,Fwearinga pale blue silk dress with a
OL,16,Fround neck, black suede mule shoes
OL,17,Fwith straps across the front and an
OL,18,Fopen toe, size 5 or 6, a cream single-
OL,19,Fbreasted, long-sleeved jacket and a
OL,20,Fblack satchel-type handbag.
OL,26,@nD@AOUtD@AOU
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
OL,2,W,.!+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
