PN,43808
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1772809879
OL,3,CNational TV appeal to feature cold
OL,4,Ccase murder of Melanie Hall
OL,6,F"In Melanie's handbag were cosmetics
OL,7,Fand a Midland cheque book and bank
OL,8,Fcard. Also missing are items of
OL,9,Fjewellery, including a Next watch with
OL,10,Fan expanding bracelet and silver drop
OL,11,Fearrings."
OL,13,FSince taking over the investigation in
OL,14,F2025, DCI Lavender has held a root and
OL,15,Fbranch review into the case.
OL,26,@nD@AOUsD@JO]
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/10
