CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F438A1772809879
OL,3,CNational TV appeal to feature cold
OL,4,Ccase murder of Melanie Hall
OL,6,FThis includes digitalising all files
OL,7,Fand exhibits onto our major incident
OL,8,Fdatabase, reviewing almost 100 hours
OL,9,Fof CCTV, revisiting key witnesses to
OL,10,Fcheck whether the information they
OL,11,Fprovided remains the same, as well as
OL,12,Fcapitalising on any forensic
OL,13,Fadvancements or opportunities to use
OL,14,FAI in the future.
OL,16,FOfficers say anyone with information
OL,17,Fcan report it through a designated
OL,18,Fappeal page on the Major Incident
OL,19,FPublic Portal or call 101 and say you
OL,20,Fhave information for the Operation
OL,21,FDenmark team.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/10
